headline: BNSF, NS, Northwestern ports trim 3 days from intermodal speed service to Chicago
summary: A partnership of BNSF, Norfolk Southern and the Northwest Seaport Alliance are offering expedited service from the Pacific Northwest to the Chicago rail hub. The post BNSF, NS, Northwestern ports trim 3 days from intermodal speed service to Chicago appeared first on FreightWaves.
